data.description: This spacious manufactured home situated on a nice over 6 acre lot offers 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, large living room plus a family room w/fireplace off the spacious kitchen, a storage building and lots of new including all new interior paint, back deck, flooring, light fixtures, some bathroom fixtures, well pump and tank and water conditioner. All of this plus a great location approximately 1 mile off SR 93. If you're looking for country but convenient, you won't want to miss out on this well priced property!!
